To get this all and ready to play...

Put the commlink.bsp and .res file in the folder:
steam/steamapps/accountname/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

Copy eveything in the materials, and paste it in:
steam/steamapps/accountname/counter-strike source/cstrike/materials

Then eveything should be good... enjoy!

-Gunslinger
